channel.title: Sites what Have Rs-Rsc in there title
channel.description:
Hello,
Well speaking to Jacmob today rsbot.org was shut down because of the site domain was evading runescape's copy right's (Runescape Bot) is what the domain meant and because of that two letters rsbot.org domain was taken off the owner of rsbot..
Ways around this, JaGeX has to email you first asking what the "rs" or "rsc" w/e stands for in the domain and if you return with Retard Sick Cunts or Retards silly they can not do anything but ignoring the email's will lead to JaGeX allowing to take your domain..
Preety stupid the internet laws right?
